name: Pre
description: PopulateChunkEvent.Pre is fired just before a chunk is populated a terrain feature. This event is fired just before terrain feature generation in ChunkProviderEnd#populate(IChunkProvider, int, int), ChunkProviderGenerate#populate(IChunkProvider, int, int), and ChunkProviderHell#populate(IChunkProvider, int, int). This event is not Cancelable . This event does not have a result. Event.HasResult This event is fired on the MinecraftForge#EVENT_BUS .
